    "body": "Did some initial investigation and it seems that the issue is due to `load_contracts` not extending the abis with those specified in `targetInterface`. https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/blob/a1f5842c62a5fdd6f6b52cc2a852d2cca7e73f47/crates/evm/src/fuzz/invariant/mod.rs#L135\r\n\r\nSo it fails to find the function. Clearly an oversight when I initially developed `targetInterface` helper. I will investigate how to pass the extended abi down the stack. ",
