    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "In case anyone needs to decode a trace, here is a trick:\r\nYou can deploy the contract with a desired interface and after that, change the bytecode at that address to any desired one. The forge will use an old contract interface for the trace decoding.\r\n\r\n```\r\nfunction _deployCallStorageHandler() internal returns(address payable) {\r\n        Reentrant reentrantToReplace = new Reentrant();\r\n        deployCodeTo(\"./CallStorageHandler.sol\", address(reentrantToReplace));\r\n        return payable(address(reentrantToReplace));\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\nI do not recommend using this approach though.",
